data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Brycewood Community! This move-in ready gem boasts 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects spacious living areas. The kitchen features a convenient island, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast area, and a dedicated dining space - ideal for both casual meals and entertaining guests.    Venture upstairs to discover a bonus loft, providing additional flexible space for your lifestyle needs. The expansive primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a generous walk-in closet and a private bath featuring a double vanity and a relaxing garden tub.    Step outside to your large private fenced backyard, creating a perfect oasis for outdoor gatherings, playtime, or simply unwinding after a busy day. Plus, you'll enjoy the convenience of being just across the street from the neighborhood pool, perfect for cooling off on warm summer days.    This home is not only a haven of comfort but also strategically located close to shopping and restaurants, adding to the overall convenience and desirability of the property. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
